==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cockshy
<hw>Cock"shy`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A game
in which trinkets are set upon sticks, to be thrown at by the players;
-- so called from an ancient popular sport which consisted in
⟦ldquo⟧shying⟦rdquo⟧ or throwing cudgels at live cocks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An object at which stones are flung.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>⟦ldquo⟧Making a <qex>cockshy</qex> of him,⟦rdquo⟧ replied the
hideous small boy.</q> <rj><qau>Dickens.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cockspur</ent>⟦br⟧
